<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Singer Michael Jackson will go ahead with a
planned British tour despite quarantine laws banning his pet
chimpanzee Bubbles, his record company says.
   Jackson was allowed to take the ape into Japan last year and he
would have liked to bring him to Britain, Jonathan Morrish of CBS
