repeatedly with a scissors at her home in Livingston, Texas.
   Ms. Carpenter survived long enough to give police a description
of her attacker.
   The 5th U.S. Circuit Court of Appeals previously rejected
Penry's arguments and upheld his murder conviction and death
sentence.
   The case is Penry vs. McCotter, 87-6177.
