<1ST_LINE>a a BC-Wheel-CavalierBox Adv09-10   06-30 0133</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-Wheel-Cavalier Box, Adv 09-10,0148</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>$Adv09</NOTE>
<NOTE>$Adv10</NOTE>
<HEAD>Advance for Weekend Editions, July 09-10, and Thereafter</HEAD>
<HEAD>With Behind The Wheel, b0691</HEAD>
